title: 199: What If Our Dogs Died? | Ear Biscuits Ep. 199
description:
A close call encounter with both of their dogs leads R&L to discuss the inevitable 'what if' of when their beloved canines are no longer with them. Listen to their recent scares and the heartwarming relationships they have with Barbara and Jade in this episode of Ear Biscuits!
